00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:41.260
So in my view, at least, how

97
00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:44.590
did cell therapy diverge from gene therapy?

98
00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:49.620
In the following ways. So firstly, the issue of efficacy.

99
00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:51.340
Okay, so quantity versus quality.

100
00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:55.080
Then we'll talk about biology and then about safety.So efficacy

101
00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:57.510
