00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:32.900
of course, are head-to-head. But the thrust of it, nonetheless, is that as you

112
00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:36.460
infuse cells that have been less manipulated ex vivo, going from what used to be

113
00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:40.220
the standard of three weeks of ex vivo expansion to

