00:07:36.010 --> 00:07:38.120
upregulated on T cells when you activate them.

131
00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:38.740
And so

132
00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:43.540
since the LDLR is low or absent, the assumption was that VSVG

