00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:53.260
one of its co-receptor, CXCR4 or CCR5.

153
00:08:53.340 --> 00:08:55.660
So clearly, the system is exquisitely specific.

154
00:08:56.820 --> 00:09:00.700
And as I mentioned to you, in the case of-- we don't use the standard pseudotyping

