00:27:36.796 --> 00:27:38.096
So they're getting lymphodepletion.

478
00:27:38.376 --> 00:27:38.656
I'm sorry?

479
00:27:38.936 --> 00:27:40.156
That's with lymphodepletion.

480
00:27:40.976 --> 00:27:42.336
Maybe. But I think that

481
00:27:44.236 --> 00:27:45.916
you might be right. I think it's entirely possible.

482
00:27:45.956 --> 00:27:49.516
But there's also the possibility, and this is, I suppose,

483
00:27:49.596 --> 00:27:50.436
my bias.

484
00:27:51.816 --> 00:27:55.686
When you cross-link CD3, as both of those products did,

485
00:27:55.726 --> 00:27:57.596
and particularly the

486
00:27:58.596 --> 00:28:02.266
case you're talking about, the viral-like particles clearly

487
00:28:02.276 --> 00:28:06.116
cross-link CD3. And that's probably why there's such good activation

488
00:28:06.216 --> 00:28:06.546
and

489
00:28:08.796 --> 00:28:10.066
proliferation of those cells.

490
00:28:11.176 --> 00:28:15.136
We know what happens when you cross-link CD3 in a dish, and there's also a drug

491
00:28:15.156 --> 00:28:18.996
that does that in patients. It causes this toxicity.

492
00:28:19.316 --> 00:28:23.096
So we don't know, I think, which one of those reactions it is.

493
00:28:23.836 --> 00:28:24.276
Okay.

494
00:28:24.576 --> 00:28:28.416
But to the larger point that I think you're making, absolutely.

495
00:28:28.496 --> 00:28:32.416
Well, let me take half a step back, which is when I saw that

496
00:28:32.456 --> 00:28:36.096
data, I thought, "This is not as safe as I was expecting it to be."

497
00:28:36.486 --> 00:28:36.486
Right.

498
00:28:36.486 --> 00:28:38.416
And I think maybe on that, we agree.

499
00:28:38.976 --> 00:28:42.436
You approach a half measure of

500
00:28:42.476 --> 00:28:44.676
lymphodepletion. Maybe a little.

501
00:28:44.796 --> 00:28:48.276
Is that possible? You need the cells,

502
00:28:48.436 --> 00:28:50.556
but is there some way to attenuate

503
00:28:51.456 --> 00:28:51.575
that?

504
00:28:51.616 --> 00:28:55.046
I think first we should find out what the cause-- And again, I'll

505
00:28:55.696 --> 00:28:55.996
tell you,

506
00:28:57.716 --> 00:29:00.756
well, not through published observations, but that

507
00:29:01.776 --> 00:29:03.856
means of transducing cells that

508
00:29:03.896 --> 00:29:07.436
are not based on

509
00:29:07.476 --> 00:29:08.536
CD3 cross-linking

510
00:29:09.496 --> 00:29:10.696
do not cause this toxicity.

511
00:29:11.056 --> 00:29:11.956
Okay. Very good. Thank you.

512
00:29:12.336 --> 00:29:12.436
There

513
00:29:15.196 --> 00:29:19.046
has to be some context placed. The lupus patients that

514
00:29:19.076 --> 00:29:21.256
