00:50:01.752 --> 00:50:04.002
rare pediatric indication with one CAR.

875
00:50:04.332 --> 00:50:04.612
So-

876
00:50:04.652 --> 00:50:05.102
Thanks for that

877
00:50:05.102 --> 00:50:06.932
... if rituximab does it, we're going to stick with that.

878
00:50:06.992 --> 00:50:07.392
Thank you.

879
00:50:07.452 --> 00:50:08.352
Thank you. Go ahead.

880
00:50:09.072 --> 00:50:11.112
Hi. Thanks for a great talk. Ben from Mass General.

