00:51:55.692 --> 00:51:59.272
group. What would you say would be the next big step for

913
00:51:59.332 --> 00:52:01.792
CCSU with maybe this

914
00:52:02.632 --> 00:52:02.992
trial?

915
00:52:03.292 --> 00:52:04.992
I don't know. We can talk about that offline.

916
00:52:05.192 --> 00:52:05.412
Okay.

917
00:52:05.592 --> 00:52:06.232
Thank you, Anne Marie.

918
00:52:06.912 --> 00:52:07.651
Last question.

919
00:52:07.832 --> 00:52:11.612
Yes, Andreas Poser, Medicine. So did you measure the GD2 binding

